1
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:14,040
Why is His Majesty with this boy again?

2
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:15,100
Go and protect him.

3
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:21,040
Senior.

4
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:25,560
Are we close in the sect?

5
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:26,840
Of course.

6
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:29,320
That's why we're on a mission together.

7
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:31,770
Then can I call you brother?

8
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:38,840
I'm sorry.

9
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:42,240
I just thought of my brother.

10
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:44,320
He's a bit like you.

11
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:47,640
He's a bit silly, but he's also very honest.

12
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,280
Where is he?

13
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,520
(He's home.)

14
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,640
He's found his home.

15
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,920
I trust your brother.

16
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,970
is watching you from above.

17
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:30,240
You are not alone.

18
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:35,720
Ah Ji.

19
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,850
Do you have a family?

20
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,560
Yes, I do.

21
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,960
But our relationship

22
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,090
is hard to describe.

23
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,200
I have a brother.

24
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:55,840
My father...

25
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:03,520
My father likes my brother more than me.

26
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,720
And my brother

27
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,320
never treated me as his family.

28
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,080
It's okay.

29
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,760
We're brothers from now on.

30
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,560
By the way,

31
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,860
How old are you?

32
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,240
Just 17.

33
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,730
You're going to be the top soon.

34
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,930
Have you figured out how to celebrate?

35
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,360
You don't even have a surname.

36
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,810
